Item Name: TimeCutter MX5050 50 in. 24.5 HP Fabricated Deck V-Twin Gas Dual Hydrostatic Riding Zero Turn Mower with Smart Speed
Description: Experience a residential zero-turn riding mower with the reliability, durability and cutting features of a commercial mower.  The Toro TimeCutter MX5050 is powered by a 24.5 HP at 3,600 RPMs Toro Commercial V-Twin engine (708 cc). It dominates challenging cutting conditions with the tough, commercial IronForged cutting system, including a 50 in. heavy-duty 10-Gauge steel fabricated mowing system and durable 6 in. cast blade spindles and reinforced leading edge. Choose from 7 height of cut positions to get a professional looking cut and tackle large acreage areas. Large 20 in. x 10 in. rear tires give you the traction you need in a variety of conditions. This lawnmower is easy to drive with the Smart Speed control system. You'll have easy control and maneuvering with the trim, tow and mow speed ranges. Enjoy the ride with maximum comfort with the 18 in. thickly padded premium seat and an anti-vibration floor mat. For easy adjustments use the foot lift assist deck height pedal. A hitch comes standard for pulling lawn and garden attachments.

Description: The Toro TimeCutter SS4225 zero-turn mower is powered by a 22.5 HP Toro Commercial engine (708cc). It has a 42 in. 2-bladed mowing system under a 4 in. deep top discharge deck with convenient washout ports.
